results.name: G.f.: A(x) = product_{k>=1}(1 + x^k)^(-lambda(k)) where lambda(k) is the Liouville function, A008836.
mathematica: nmax = 80; lambda[k_Integer?Positive] := If[ k > 1, (-1)^Total[ Part[Transpose[FactorInteger[k]], 2] ], 1 ]; CoefficientList[ Series[ Product[ (1 + x^k)^(-lambda[k]), {k, 1, nmax} ], {x, 0, nmax} ], x ]
